{"article_id":"A2DxMBlekS9fj7QM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Get all the latest news on coronavirus and more delivered daily to your inbox .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Sign up here .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Dr. Anthony Fauci , the face of the White House coronavirus task force , warned in testimony Tuesday before the Senate Health Committee","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that reopening the economy","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"before certain `` checkpoints ''","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"set up in the Trump administration 's coronavirus recovery plan","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"are met","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"could bring `` serious '' consequences .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"`` As I have said many times publicly ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"what we have worked out is a guideline framework","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"for how to open America again , \"","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"Fauci said ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"referencing a set of guidelines","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"the White House has released","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"for states and localities to begin opening their economies .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"In order to proceed to the first of three stages ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"states would need to see an uninterrupted decrease in coronavirus cases over a 14-day period .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"`` Depending on the dynamics of an outbreak in a particular region , state , city or area ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that would really determine the speed and the pace","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"with which one does reenter or reopen , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Fauci said .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"`` If some areas","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"- cities states or what have you -","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"jump over those barriers , checkpoints","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"and prematurely open up","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"without having the capability","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"of being able to respond effectively , and efficiently ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"my concern is that we will start to see little spikes","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that might turn into outbreaks . ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"GOP SEN. ALEXANDER :","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"'STAYING AT HOME INDEFINITELY IS NOT THE SOLUTION '","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Fauci warned","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that prematurely lifting coronavirus restrictions","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"closing schools and businesses and limiting travel","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"would lead to `` suffering and death ''","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"and `` turn the clock back","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"instead of going forward . ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"When asked by Sen. Patty Murray , D-Wash. ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"what could happen","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"if areas do ignore the `` checkpoints , ''","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Fauci said ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` The consequences could be really serious . ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Further , when asked by Sen. Elizabeth Warren , D-Mass. ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"if the virus was under control ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Fauci said","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"it is not .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"`` Right now it depends on what you mean by containment , ''","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"Fauci said ,","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"noting","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"the virus is not completely under control .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"`` So","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"when you look at the dynamics of new cases ,","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"even though some are coming down ,","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"the curve looks flat","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"with some coming down .","depth":15},{"id":55,"text":"So I think","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"we 're going in the right direction ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"but the right direction does not mean we have by any means total control of this outbreak . ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"without proper measures ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"the U.S. could face a `` resurgence '' in cases .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"the U.S. should be in a much better place by the fall ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"but said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"if adequate measures are not taken ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"`` there will be problems . ''","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"`` The time for magical thinking is over here , ''","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Warren said of President Trump 's pushes","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"to reopen the economy quickly","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"and optimism","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"that the virus `` will go away . ''","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"The hearing ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"which features Fauci , the director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"( NIAID ) ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"as well as three other top administration health officials ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"is the biggest congressional hearing","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"since the coronavirus crisis began .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"It comes","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"as states across the country are plotting their own courses","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"for reopening their economies ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"with some already opening sectors","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and others maintaining strict lockdowns .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"President Trump himself has stressed the importance","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"of getting America back to work ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"leading to criticism from some Democrats","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"that this approach could be too risky .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Fauci did not rip on the Trump administration 's response to the pandemic in his planned remarks ,","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"instead emphasizing efforts by the National Institutes of Health","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"( NIH )","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"to develop vaccines and other medical means","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"to fight the coronavirus .","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"NATIONAL PARK SERVICE TESTS REOPENING ,","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"PREPS VISITORS FOR 'NEW NORMAL ' :","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"HERE 'S WHAT TO EXPECT `","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"` Hopefully our research efforts , together with the other public health efforts , will get us quickly to an end to this terrible ordeal","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"that we are all going through , ''","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Fauci said .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"`` NIH is focused on developing safe and effective COVID-19 vaccines and therapeutics , and sensitive , specific , and rapid point-of-care diagnostic tests , ''","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Fauci also said in written remarks","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"submitted to the committee .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"`` These efforts will improve our response to the current pandemic","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"and bolster our preparedness for the next , inevitable emerging disease outbreak ''","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"FAUCI , OTHER HEALTH OFFICIALS TO TESTIFY BEFORE SENATE PANEL VIA VIDEOCONFERENCE AMID CORONAVIRUS CONCERNS","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"On one point , Fauci said","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"the government is focusing on several different vaccine candidates ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"using the hockey term `` multiple shots on goal ''","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"to describe the increased chances","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"that one would work .","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"Additionally , he said","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"if more than one is successful","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"that would help increase the availability of the vaccines globally .","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"But ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Fauci noted ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"`` there 's no guarantee","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"that a vaccine is going to be effective . ''","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Given the chance","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"to attack Trump in an exchange with Sen. Tim Kaine , D-Va. ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"Fauci declined to .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Kaine pushed Fauci on","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"whether South Korea 's success","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"on fighting the coronavirus","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"showed","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"that the U.S. response to the pandemic was inadequate .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"Fauci noted","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"that there is a `` big difference '' between the U.S. and South Korea .","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"Fauci appeared remotely due to concerns","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"that he might have been exposed to the coronavirus .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Multiple senators also appeared virtually for the hearing ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"including Sen. Lamar Alexander , R-Tenn. , the chairman of the committee , and Murray , the ranking member .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"`` After consulting with Dr. Fauci ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"and in an abundance of caution for our witnesses , senators , and the staff ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"all four Administration witnesses will appear by videoconference due to these unusual circumstances , ''","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Alexander said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Alexander , in his opening remarks , emphasized the necessity of testing","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"and also said","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"the government might make an effort to mass-manufacture a vaccine","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"before it ' s been proven to work","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"so it can be quickly distributed","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"once it ' s officially approved .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"DR. ANTHONY FAUCI :","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"CORONAVIRUS TESTING AVAILABILITY , SPEED WILL PLAY PART IN FOOTBALL 'S RETURN","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"\" Those vaccines , those treatments , are the ultimate solution , \"","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"\" But until we have them ,","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"all roads back to work and school go through testing . ''","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"Murray wasted no time","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"hitting the president in her opening remarks .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"`` Families across the country are counting on us for the truth about the COVID-19 pandemic ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"especially since it is clear they will not get it from President Trump , ''","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"`` Truth is essential ...","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"The president is n't telling the truth .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"We must .","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"And our witnesses must . ''","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"STEAK ' N SHAKE PERMANENTLY CLOSES NEARLY 10 PERCENT OF ITS RESTAURANTS AMID CORONAVIRUS CRISIS","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"She also criticized the Trump administration 's tangible response to the virus ,","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"it has been marked by delays and insufficient assistance to states and health professionals .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"Additionally , she advocated for another coronavirus stimulus bill","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"to help ease the burden of the economic shutdowns across the country","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"aimed at slowing the spread of the virus .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"Fauci ,","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"when questioned by Alexander ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"it would not be reasonable to expect a vaccine to be ready for back-to-school season this year .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Trump has said","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"he would like to have a vaccine by the end of the year .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"`` The idea","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"of having treatments or a vaccine ... ready by the fall ...","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"would be something of a bridge too far , ''","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"RED LOBSTER CUSTOMERS TURNED AWAY DUE TO LARGE VOLUME OF MOTHER 'S DAY ORDERS","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"Fauci also added","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"that there is a good chance","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"to see further rebounds in the disease ,","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"but that he hopes","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"the U.S. will be better prepared to deal with them .","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"`` I would hope","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"if we do have the threat of a second wave ,","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"we will be able to deal with it very effectively","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"to prevent it from becoming an outbreak .","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"Not only what we 've seen now ,","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"but much , much less , ''","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"Admiral Brett Giroir , the Assistant Secretary for Health , emphasized","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"that the U.S. had conducted `` more than 9 million COVID-19 tests , a number far greater than any other country and double the per capita tests","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"performed to date in South Korea , '' a nation","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"that many have held up as the model","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"for handling the coronavirus ' effects .","depth":14},{"id":191,"text":"He noted","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"that by the late summer and early fall , he expected the U.S. to be able to perform between 40 and 50 million coronavirus tests per month .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"Fauci got into a dustup with Sen. Rand Paul , R-Ky. , over Paul 's criticism of some of the prognostications","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"that have come from public health experts","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"and the push","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"to reopen schools quickly .","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"`` The history of this will be wrong prediction after wrong prediction after wrong predicition , ''","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"Paul said ,","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"mentioning , among several other examples , Sweden ,","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"which left its schools open .","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"you 're an end-all ,","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"I do n't think","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"you 're the one person","depth":15},{"id":205,"text":"that gets to make a decision . ''","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"`` I have never made myself out to be the end-all and only voice in this , ''","depth":14},{"id":207,"text":"Fauci said .","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":"`` I 'm a scientist , a physician and a public health official .","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"I give advice ,","depth":15},{"id":210,"text":"according to the best scientific evidence . ''","depth":15},{"id":211,"text":"He continued ,","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"emphasizing","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"that it is not clear children are generally immune from the harmful effects of the coronavirus :","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"`` We should be humble about what we do n't know .","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"And I think","depth":16},{"id":216,"text":"that falls under the fact","depth":17},{"id":217,"text":"that we do n't know everything about this virus ,","depth":17},{"id":218,"text":"and we really got to be very careful ,","depth":16},{"id":219,"text":"particularly when it comes to children .","depth":16},{"id":220,"text":"Because","depth":15},{"id":221,"text":"the more and more we learn ,","depth":16},{"id":222,"text":"we 're seeing things about what this virus can do","depth":17},{"id":223,"text":"that we did n't see from the studies in China or in Europe . ''","depth":17},{"id":224,"text":"During questioning , self-proclaimed Democratic socialist Sen. Bernie Sanders , I-Vt. , pushed the witnesses on whether or not a vaccine ,","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"once developed ,","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"would be broadly available to people","depth":12},{"id":227,"text":"regardless of their income .","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"`` If , God-willing , a vaccine is developed ,","depth":14},{"id":229,"text":"and if we 're able to produce it as quickly","depth":15},{"id":230,"text":"as we all hope","depth":16},{"id":231,"text":"we can ,","depth":16},{"id":232,"text":"I imagine","depth":14},{"id":233,"text":"that that vaccine would be distributed to all people free of charge ,","depth":15},{"id":234,"text":"or at least make sure that everybody in America","depth":18},{"id":235,"text":"that needs that vaccine","depth":18},{"id":236,"text":"will get it","depth":17},{"id":237,"text":"regardless of their income ? ''","depth":16},{"id":238,"text":"Sanders asked Food and Drug Administration Commissioner Stephen Hahn .","depth":12},{"id":239,"text":"Hahn said","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"that issue was not under his purview as the FDA commissioner ,","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"but Giroir said","depth":14},{"id":242,"text":"he would advocate within the Trump administration to make sure","depth":15},{"id":243,"text":"the vaccine is accessible .","depth":15},{"id":244,"text":"`` They should gain access to it ...","depth":15},{"id":245,"text":"I will certainly advocate","depth":16},{"id":246,"text":"that everyone is able to receive the vaccine","depth":17},{"id":247,"text":"regardless of income or any other circumstance , ''","depth":17},{"id":248,"text":"Hahn said .","depth":14},{"id":249,"text":"Democrats , ahead of the hearing , made clear","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"they saw it as an opportunity","depth":13},{"id":251,"text":"to separate Fauci from President Trump ,","depth":14},{"id":252,"text":"whom the medical expert is almost always with","depth":15},{"id":253,"text":"when he appears publicly ,","depth":15},{"id":254,"text":"so that Fauci will feel free to criticize Trump .","depth":11},{"id":255,"text":"Critics of the president have argued","depth":14},{"id":256,"text":"his response to the coronavirus crisis was wholly inadequate ,","depth":14},{"id":257,"text":"alleging","depth":14},{"id":258,"text":"Trump initially downplayed the threat","depth":15},{"id":259,"text":"before letting petty politics get in the way","depth":17},{"id":260,"text":"of helping states","depth":17},{"id":261,"text":"and then moving too quickly","depth":17},{"id":262,"text":"to reopen the economy .","depth":17},{"id":263,"text":"`` Until now , we 've mostly heard from the members of the coronavirus task force through the distorted lens of the White House press conference","depth":15},{"id":264,"text":"where the president often prevents them from answering fully ,","depth":16},{"id":265,"text":"interrupts their response ,","depth":17},{"id":266,"text":"or even contradicts their fact-based evidence , ''","depth":17},{"id":267,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , said on Monday .","depth":14},{"id":268,"text":"`` This will be one of the first opportunities","depth":17},{"id":269,"text":"for Dr. Fauci to tell the American people the unvarnished truth","depth":17},{"id":270,"text":"without the president lurking over his shoulder .","depth":16},{"id":271,"text":"Dr. Fauci , let it rip , ''","depth":15},{"id":272,"text":"he added .","depth":14},{"id":273,"text":"Trump previously blocked Fauci from appearing before a House committee ,","depth":13},{"id":274,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":275,"text":"the members of the Democrat-controlled House are `` haters . ''","depth":14},{"id":276,"text":"Fauci ,","depth":15},{"id":277,"text":"like he had previously ,","depth":15},{"id":278,"text":"avoided criticizing Trump directly on Tuesday ,","depth":14},{"id":279,"text":"but did issue stern warnings on what could happen","depth":14},{"id":280,"text":"if measures","depth":16},{"id":281,"text":"to slow the disease 's spread","depth":16},{"id":282,"text":"are lifted too soon .","depth":15},{"id":283,"text":"Under questioning from Sen. Kelly Loeffler , R-Ga. , all four witnesses said","depth":12},{"id":284,"text":"their relationships with the president are not `` confrontational ''","depth":12},{"id":285,"text":"and said","depth":12},{"id":286,"text":"they felt free to give their opinions and advice on the coronavirus pandemic .","depth":12},{"id":287,"text":"Fauci was joined by Dr. Robert Redfield , the director of the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention , Hahn and Giroir .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":575,"left":289,"right":574,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":289,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":574,"left":378,"right":573,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":378,"left":358,"right":377,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":358,"left":315,"right":357,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":301,"right":314,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":294,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":2,"right":293,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":293,"left":292,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":3,"right":291,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":290,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":297,"right":299,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":296,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"lef